description: The iShares Edge MSCI EM Value Factor UCITS ETF aims to track the performance of an index composed of large- and mid-capitalization stocks from emerging markets, which demonstrate high value characteristics: comparing the price of equity to estimated future earnings; the price of equity relative to book value; and enterprise value of a company relative to its operating cash flow.
name: iShares Edge MSCI EM Value Factor UCITS ETF
